Prof. Burkett is one of the best stats profs at uottawa! Though math stats is very hard, she does her best to give clear explanations for each topic, as well as lots of examples. Homeworks were very difficult however she grades very generously and usually grades only the easier questions. Tests were very fair. 10/10!

Honestly a really good professor - Stats can be complicated/boring at times but she does her best to stick to the basics and explains things well. Textbook is crucial for clarification and for practice questions. Assignments are an easy boost. Midterm and exam were both fair, but the wording can sometimes be tricky. Would recommend for sure!
